    Bridge->>EAS: getAttestation(uid)
    EAS-->>Bridge: attestation (revocationTime ≠ 0)
    Bridge-->>Token: FALSE ❌
    Token-->>Bob: TRANSFER BLOCKED

    Note over CO,Bob: Bob cannot trade until re-verified with a new attestation

